PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1999-483 of March 23, 1999, appointing HELEN MAMAYAOK MAKSAGAK, as Commissioner of Nunavut, by replacing the phrase "and fixes her salary at the rate set out in the schedule hereto" with the phrase "and fixes her salary and other conditions of employment according to the schedule hereto".
